WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.460
This report is really astonishing,

00:00:02.460 --> 00:00:07.780
since you propose a large autonomy regarding space research and development

00:00:07.780 --> 00:00:11.960
but you make an unbelievable statement 
a few lines further down,

00:00:11.960 --> 00:00:19.700
when you say that the EU thus strengthens its cooperation and coordination with NATO

00:00:19.700 --> 00:00:21.780
- we call it OTAN in my country -

00:00:21.780 --> 00:00:29.240
and with the USA, calling both the wardens of security and stability in Europe â€” the USA!

00:00:29.240 --> 00:00:35.440
Right after stating that the USA holds secret prisons in Europe where people are tortured!

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:37.020
This is absurd!

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:41.400
The task of the European Union has to be the demilitarization of space

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:45.280
because it is the next frontier, and even today's frontier of mankind,

00:00:45.280 --> 00:00:50.940
and the multiplication of military engines 
and methods of control in space is not a good thing,

00:00:50.940 --> 00:00:53.140
all the more so because you ended your speech saying

00:00:53.140 --> 00:00:58.000
that you intend to control the boats that take 
refugees on board. All this is absurd!

